Spark 360
https://code.google.com/p/spark360/
===============================================

Spark 360 is a gaming client for Android and iOS. It's currently available 
on Google Play, and supports Xbox Live and PlayStation Network. 
The app allows you to monitor your achievements, trophies, friends' 
statuses, and includes many other features, such as trophy/achievement
comparisons, messaging (Xbox Live), home screen widgets, notifications, 
and more.

Spark 360 is an unofficial application, and not supported, endorsed, or 
affiliated with Microsoft Corporation or Sony Corporation.

Please see COPYING for license information.

